import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom/client"; // import for router
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"; //import for router
import "./index.css";
import App from "./App";
import Layout from "./layout/Layout";
import Wokal from "./pages/Wokal";
import Gitary from "./pages/Gitary";
import LoginPage from "./pages/LoginPage";
import ONas from "./pages/ONas";
import Kalendarz from "./pages/Kalendarz";
import UstawieniaKonta from "./pages/UstawieniaKonta";
import Pomoc from "./pages/Pomoc";
import Dj from "./pages/Dj";
import InstrumentySmyczkowe from "./pages/InstrumentySmyczkowe";

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root")).render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    {/* <RouterProvider router={router} /> */}
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<App />} />
        </Route>

        <Route path="/login" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<LoginPage />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/o-nas" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<ONas />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/kalendarz" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Kalendarz />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/ustawienia-konta" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<UstawieniaKonta />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/pomoc" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Pomoc />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/gitary" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Gitary />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/wokal" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Wokal />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/gitary" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Gitary />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/wokal" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Wokal />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/gitary" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Gitary />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/instrumenty-smyczkowe" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<InstrumentySmyczkowe />} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/dj" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route index element={<Dj />} />
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  </React.StrictMode>
);
